{"tid":1011672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"增撥 5 億予醫管局　林鄭：從沒說過能解決問題　撥款為對前線展關懷","createTime":"2019-02-07T03:25:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T04:34:58.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7974f0b4d845f0d8c1d40e81eef04b195ed21443","tid":1011672,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:25:20.000Z","msg":"香港公共醫療迫爆問題，政府早前宣布預留5億元撥款予醫管局，應付人手不足問題。特首林鄭月娥今日表示，從沒說過五億元能解決問題，稱額外撥款是為了展示對前線醫護人員的支持及關懷。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥今早到機場出席新春活動並會見記者，她表示無論去年額外撥五億給醫管局，或今年額外五億元，「我從沒有說過，這樣撥出五億元能解決香港公營醫療系統面對問題」。她表示面對冬季流感高峰，額外撥款五億元是為了展示對前線醫護人員的支持及關懷。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又指，人手問題難以在短期內解決，培訓醫生需要多年時間，政府已增加醫科生數目以增加醫療人手。她指任何地方的醫療系統，若過分以醫院、治療作主導，都會產生問題。因此現屆政府強調要做好基層醫療、檢查服務等，減少不必要的入院。<br />\n<br />\n對於沙中綫接連爆出工程問題，林鄭表示過去一年沙中綫項目出了很多問題，引起社會關注。特區政府非常重視，也很嚴厲調查跟進有關沙中線工程問題，「大前提一定要確保安全，我們才會開通這條沙中綫」。她指在獨立調查委員會稍後發表報告中，如果顯示應有更進一步調查，特區政府一定會嚴肅跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E5%A2%9E%E6%92%A5-5-%E5%84%84%E4%BA%88%E9%86%AB%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E5%BE%9E%E6%B2%92%E8%AA%AA%E9%81%8E%E8%83%BD%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E7%82%BA%E5%B0%8D%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E5%B1%95%E9%97%9C%E6%87%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25A2%259E%25E6%2592%25A5-5-%25E5%2584%2584%25E4%25BA%2588%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E5%25BE%259E%25E6%25B2%2592%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%2583%25BD%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C-%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%25B1%2595%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2587%25B7%2F&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=cad4e177\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25A2%259E%25E6%2592%25A5-5-%25E5%2584%2584%25E4%25BA%2588%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E5%25BE%259E%25E6%25B2%2592%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%2583%25BD%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C-%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%25B1%2595%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2587%25B7%2F&h=17bbecfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E5%A2%9E%E6%92%A5-5-%E5%84%84%E4%BA%88%E9%86%AB%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E5%BE%9E%E6%B2%92%E8%AA%AA%E9%81%8E%E8%83%BD%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E7%82%BA%E5%B0%8D%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E5%B1%95%E9%97%9C%E6%87%B7/</a>"},{"pid":"eb9d445af1b79894b650eb9c4a25f1b833fc29ed","tid":1011672,"uid":120837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:35:30.000Z","msg":"唔係為解決問題，咁你俾黎把撚啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4b6b2544b0ddbe440228a5f4adca31f0c31fcc","tid":1011672,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb9d445af1b79894b650eb9c4a25f1b833fc29ed","tid":1011672,"uid":120837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:35:30.000Z","msg":"唔係為解決問題，咁你俾黎把撚啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:43:03.000Z","msg":"做show <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8384df1c4865194dbb17d92873a0b68149a99e","tid":1011672,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:45:28.000Z","msg":"五億？<br />\n直頭要一萬五千億落去就差唔多 <br />\n起少個支那島"},{"pid":"20bac3b72833a0e53e476d7fe3cf35dade7ea67e","tid":1011672,"uid":46170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:45:39.000Z","msg":"佢都好意思講出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52708803b1a5248d44e386250625848dd53891b4","tid":1011672,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T04:34:58.000Z","msg